# No Automatic File Modifications

Do not modify files unless I explicitly instruct you to do so.

Specifically:
- Do not use edit tools.
- Do not apply patches.
- Do not update files automatically.
- Do not refactor files proactively.

You may:
- Explain issues
- Suggest improvements
- Show example code in chat

Only modify files if I clearly say something like:
- "apply this change"
- "update the file"
- "edit the code"
- "make the change"
- "implement this in the repo"

If unsure whether to edit files, ask for confirmation first.
